<h3 id="starling-symphony--oct-20-2023--phoenix-gallery-waterbury-vt"><strong>Starling Symphony</strong> // <em>Oct 20, 2023</em> // Phoenix Gallery, Waterbury VT</h3>

<p>Launch event for artist Trystan Bates’ <em>Starling Symphony</em> Capsule Collection. Musical performance will be an original composition in response to the five movements present in the <em>Starling Symphony</em> artwork, currently on display at The Phoenix Gallery through November.</p>

